<ext_description linkend="Elementary_boundary_representation_arm.Elementary_brep_shape_representation">
	An <b>Elementary_brep_shape_representation</b> is a type of
	<express_ref linkend="Elemental_geometric_shape:arm:Elemental_geometric_shape_arm.Geometric_model"/>
	composed of one or more manifold solid breps each of which is defined with elementary
    geometry and complete explicit topology.
    The face geometry is restricted to elementary surfaces, and the edge curves to lines, polylines
   or conics.
</ext_description>

